modules.description: This module defines a collection of module signatures for building ocamlbuild plugins, including abstractions for ordered types with printing, sets, lists, strings, tags, pathnames, commands, glob patterns, logging, outcomes, miscellaneous utilities, command-line options, architectures, Findlib integration, and plugin interfaces. It works with standard OCaml data types and domain-specific types for build systems, such as tags, pathnames, and commands. Concrete use cases include defining custom plugins for ocamlbuild that manipulate build tags, process file paths, execute commands, or extend the build system's behavior.
